{"tid":2403160,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"CPU過熱一問","createTime":"2021-02-11T02:39:22.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-11T09:26:21.000Z","uid":123102,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"1300492a25959a0a1b8980cc5b4f1c3f8f1d7bfc","tid":2403160,"uid":123102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T02:39:22.000Z","msg":"我部電腦早三年砌的, 最近自己換左motherboard+CPU再加左條M.2<br />\n部電腦靜止狀態係40-50度, <br />\n但係求其開隻LOL玩再加行緊個chrome就上到95-100度<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n想問大家有冇咩idea/我下面嘅部機嘅spec係咪唔係咁好(機箱果D)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nSPEC:<br />\nWD Blue WD10EZEX 1TB 7200rpm 64MB 3.5 Inch HDD<br />\nCrucial P2 1TB M.2 PCIe NVMe Gen 3 SSD<br />\nCorsair VS Series&trade; VS450 80Plus 450W PSU<br />\nIntel&reg; Core&trade; Comet Lake i5-10400 Processor 2.90 GHz Cache 6 Core 12 Thread LGA1200<br />\nCPU原廠散熱<br />\nAeroCool Corporate Series CS 102 M.ATX<br />\nKingston SSDNow A400 120GB TLC 2.5 Inch SATA III SSD<br />\nKLEVV DDR4 1x8GB Value Series 2400MHz CL15<br />\nGigabyte B460M GAMING HD MATX<br />\nGigabyte GeForce&reg; GTX 1060 WINDFORCE OC 3GB GDDR5"},{"pid":"b056aebadfb78cf46b1707a8f6f55748942442d4","tid":2403160,"uid":264965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T02:41:10.000Z","msg":"清一清塵先"},{"pid":"858c50e8974eca43e2ad2d586359278154922474","tid":2403160,"uid":123102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b056aebadfb78cf46b1707a8f6f55748942442d4","tid":2403160,"uid":264965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T02:41:10.000Z","msg":"清一清塵先"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T02:43:41.000Z","msg":"請晒了<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />之前換motherboard嘅時候清得好乾淨<br />\n最緊見到佢過熱都睇過, 真係冇乜塵<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"081f3105217eb3828a754fd51a4f16c824b74852","tid"